INTERPRETATION
------------------------------------------------------------------------

  ALL 10 TESTS NULL.

  Bessel zeros j₁₁, j₀₁, j₁₂, and their ratios/differences
  are algebraically independent of the HOWL transcendental basis
  {π, e, ln2, √2, √3, √5, √7, φ, ζ(3), ζ(5), Li₄(1/2),
   Catalan, γ, e^π} at 100 digits with maxcoeff 10,000.

  Prior PSLQ record: 72/72 null (DISC-6-8)
  This search:       10/10 null
